      "para_id": "Q004878.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Bau , his lady , Geme-ĝirnuna , the spouse of Amarsu , the child of Alla , dedicated this ( object ) for the well-being of Ur-Ninmarki , governor of Lagaš , and for her own well-being ."
    }
